go to ./docker folder: cd docker
run: docker-compose up -d
go to classpath folder: cd ..
run: mvn tomcat7:redeploy

STOP:
go to ./docker folder: cd docker
run: docker-compose stop

========================

with postgre:
go to ./docker/compose_postgresql folder: cd docker/compose_postgresql
run: docker-compose up -d

you should create a db "library" on localhost:8082 by login:admin pass:admin
go to classpath folder: cd ..
run: mvn tomcat7:redeploy